&lt;h1 id="something-vast-this-way-comes"&gt;Something Vast This Way Comes&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 14 2006&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="http://Vast.com"&gt;Vast.com&lt;/a&gt; (developer) Preview is finally available! If you&amp;rsquo;ve been wondering what we&amp;rsquo;ve been up to, here it is, in a nutshell – we are building a search service that extracts classified ads from across the web, structures them, and then makes them available via an open [REST API](http://REST API) for commercial and non-commercial uses.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>